query:
SELECT 
  cl.id,
  cl.customerId,
  cl.apiId,
  cl.activationId,
  cl.timestamp,
  c.name as customerName,
  c.email as customerEmail,
  sa.name as apiName
FROM cancellation_logs cl
JOIN customers c ON cl.customerId = c.id
JOIN sms_apis sa ON cl.apiId = sa.id
ORDER BY cl.timestamp DESC
LIMIT 20;
